            <div class="lang-en">
                <h2>About the journal</h2>
                <p>The journal "Economic and Humanitarian Studies of Regions" has passed the examination and confirmed the right to be included in the List of the Higher Attestation Commission: <a href="http://vak.ed.gov.ru/documents/10179/0/%CF%E5%F0%E5%F7%E5%ED%FC%20%C2%C0%CA_02.10.2017.pdf/30d136d1-42b5-4c8f-8c79-a76d04132245" target="_blank">Link</a></p>
                <p>The journal "Economic and Humanitarian Studies of Regions" is included in the New List of peer-reviewed scientific publications in which the main scientific results of dissertations for the degree of Candidate of Sciences, for the degree of Doctor of Sciences should be published (http://perechen.vak2.ed.gov.ru /) and publishes materials of original theoretical and applied research on topical issues of pedagogy, philosophy and sociology, representing of interest to the teaching staff and researchers.</p>
                <p>The journal is published in accordance with Federal legislation on Mass Media, registered with the Federal Service for Supervision of Communications, Information Technology and Mass Communications (Roskomnadzor) - registration number PI No. FSS77-39740. Subscription index in the "Combined catalog. The press of Russia. Newspapers and magazines" - 37137. The publication rules for authors were developed by the editorial board and approved by the editor-in-chief. </p>
                <p>The journal is published typographically in printed form, published 1 time every two months, has an electronic full-text version, which is identical in content to the printed form, is posted on the Internet after the next issue is published at <a href="http://cegr.ru" target="_blank">www.cegr.ru</a></p>

                <h3 class="mt-2 mb-1">Thematic areas</h3>
                <p>09.00.01 – Ontology and theory of knowledge (philosophical sciences)</p>
                <p>09.00.11 – Social Philosophy (philosophical sciences)</p>
                <p>09.00.13 – Philosophical anthropology, philosophy of culture (philosophical sciences)</p>
                <p>13.00.01 – Общая педагогика, история педагогики и образования (педагогические науки)</p>
                <p>13.00.08 – General pedagogy, history of pedagogy and education (pedagogical sciences)</p>
                <p>22.00.04 – Social structure, social institutions and processes (social sciences)</p>

